&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and train DevOps engineers, fostering a culture of accountability, high performance, and continuous learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the DevOps strategy, technical roadmap and execution across our global trading production environment, ensuring system uptime, scalability, and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain CI/CD pipelines to ensure rapid, secure, and reliable software delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead improvements in automation, deployment workflows, and monitoring systems, reducing manual effort and increasing system robustness and agility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure production readiness for new exchanges, trading strategies, and infrastructure changes, coordinating across development, trading, and infrastructure teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the team in leadership forums, advocating for production priorities, and aligning team objectives with broader business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
