&lt;li&gt;Strong development skills in Python, Golang and shell scripting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience defining and managing SLAs/SLOs, with a data-driven approach to improving reliability and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
