&lt;div data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are looking for a passionate, technically talented individual with a strong background in networking and security platforms to join our Infrastructure and Technology Service team.&amp;nbsp;The successful candidate&amp;nbsp;will work closely with our trading support and development teams to ensure that our systems deliver the required performance, availability, and security posture. &lt;strong&gt;This is an onsite role located in Hong Kong, Chicago, Shanghai or Sydney (with authorization to work in Chicago, Shanghai or Sydney).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
