&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and support enterprise network infrastructure across multiple sites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and maintain Cisco routers and switches, including configuration, upgrades, and troubleshooting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer and optimise FortiGate firewalls, including policies, routing, VPNs, VDOMs, and security profiles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage FortiManager and FortiAnalyzer for centralised configuration, logging, reporting, and ADOM management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform advanced troubleshooting across IP networks, including packet‑level analysis and protocol diagnostics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with data centre providers on cabinet layouts, power requirements, cross‑connects, and media types.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with telecommunications carriers for leased line provisioning, installation, testing, and handover.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate and support HP Synergy and Supermicro (SMC) SuperServer enclosures, including uplink design, fabric connectivity, and integration into core network infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate network documentation, diagrams, and asset records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure network security best practices and compliance with organisational standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
